The dashboard routes only use `@login_required`, not `@role_required`:

```python
@app.route('/dashboard/')
@login_required
def dashboard_index():

@app.route('/dashboard/overview')
@login_required
def dashboard_overview():

@app.route('/dashboard/reports')
@login_required
def dashboard_reports():
```

The `role_required` decorator is defined but never applied to any dashboard route. The spec requires "role-only (login required)" mode, meaning role-based access control must be enforced, but only login checking is applied to all three dashboard routes.
